sentences.english: The result of a demiurge's act of creation is a Progenitor, the prototype Promethean of a Lineage.
sentences.chinese: 造物主的作品就被稱爲先祖，也是該世系的原型。

sentences.english: Because the patriarchs were jealous of Joseph, they sold him as a slave into Egypt. But God was with him
sentences.chinese: 先祖嫉妒約瑟，把他賣到埃及去。

sentences.english: She doesn’t tell me one ofthose stories about the old ancestors.
sentences.chinese: 她不再和我述說我們以色列人先祖的事蹟了。

sentences.english: And the patriarchs, moved with envy, sold Joseph into Egypt: but God was with him
sentences.chinese: 先祖嫉妒約瑟，把他賣到埃及去。

sentences.english: Ancestral Awakening - Now works on Riptide Critical Hits.
sentences.chinese: 先祖覺醒可以被激流的暴擊觸發。

sentences.english: My ancestors also brought back the resplendent western civilization, such as medicine and calendar.
sentences.chinese: 我的先祖們也帶回了璀璨的西方文明，如醫學與歷算。

sentences.english: According to my family record, my late grandfather was a second degree candidate in the provincial examination.
sentences.chinese: 根據家譜的記載，我的先祖是清末一名舉人。

sentences.english: Does Genetic Ancestry Explain Higher Values of Glycated Hemoglobin in African Americans?
sentences.chinese: 遺傳先祖能否解釋非洲裔美國人糖化血紅素的值較高？

sentences.english: Remember too that Obed became an ancestor of Jesus.
sentences.chinese: 也別忘記，俄備得成爲了耶穌的先祖。

sentences.english: All the evidence is that she was buried with her ancestors.
sentences.chinese: 所有的證據只表明她與她的先祖們葬在了一起。

sentences.english: Even Abraham the patriarch gave him a tenth of the spoils.
sentences.chinese: 先祖亞伯拉罕將自己所擄來上等之物取十分之一給他。

sentences.english: Do not move an ancient boundary stone set up by your forefathers.
sentences.chinese: 你先祖所立的地界，你不可挪移。

sentences.english: Later Isaac became the father of Jacob, and Jacob became the father of the twelve patriarchs.
sentences.chinese: 以撒生雅各，雅各生十二位先祖。

sentences.english: People with the same surname or family clan gather at their ancestral temples to worship their ancestors in order of their ages.
sentences.chinese: 同宗同族的人們齊聚在先祖祠堂，按年齡祭拜祖先。

sentences.english: Any Prometheans the Progenitor then creates inherit his Lineage.
sentences.chinese: 由先祖製作的活屍則繼承其世系。

sentences.english: The name Yuyin (extensive shade, or benefit from ancestors) is meant to remember and perpetuate this ancestral bounty to posterity.
sentences.chinese: 爲紀念和永澤先祖福廕取“餘蔭”二字作園名。

definition: primogenitor/founder of a school or trade
